snippet.title: Wii Shop Theme - Jazz Cover || insaneintherainmusic (feat. 8BitBrigadier & Kenny Stern)
snippet.description:
Looks like Wii elevator music season isn't over yet! Relax with this bossa nova version of the Wii Shop Theme, and reflect on all the time you spent waiting for your Wii to connect to the Wii Shop online. Insaneintherainmusic's jazz cover / remix of the Wii Shop Theme, featuring 8BitBrigadier on flute and my awesome roommate Kenny Stern on Guitar!

🎷 Subscribe for more Video Game Jazz! ► http://bit.ly/insanesubscribe
❤ Support me on Patreon! ► http://bit.ly/supportinsane
🎼 Sheet Music ► https://bit.ly/31pA0HG

So many of you guys liked the Mii Channel theme, so I figured I'd give another Wii song the jazz treatment! Just like the Mii Channel theme, the Wii Shop theme is burned into my head (and into many of yours I'm sure) through sheer repetition.

I arrange, record, and produce jazz covers / remixes of video game music every other Saturday morning at 9:30 AM PST/ 12:30 PM EST on my YouTube channel! My channel combines my loves of jazz and video game music, creating covers and remixes you'll enjoy.

Originally Composed by Kazumi Totaka
